No. 27,

Orig.

Ohio v. Kentucky.

Report of Special Master, upon motion of State of Ohio, received and ordered filed. Exceptions, if any, with supporting briefs may be filed within 60 days. Reply briefs, if any, may be filed within 30 days of receipt of exceptions. [For earlier orders herein, see, e. g., 404 U. S. 933.]
